content.en: TMD Research Insights: These scientific abstracts explore various aspects of temporomandibular disorders (TMD), such as their etiology, treatment implications, and diagnostic accuracy. The research questions focus on understanding the biomechanics, stress distribution, and outcomes of TMD, as well as the role of physiotherapy and the relationship between TMD and other conditions. However, no algorithms are mentioned in these studies, indicating that the research does not attribute agency to algorithms in addressing these questions.
content.da: TMD Forskningsindsigter: Disse videnskabelige resuméer udforsker forskellige aspekter af temporomandibulære lidelser (TMD), såsom deres etiologi, behandlingseffekter og diagnostisk nøjagtighed. Forskningsspørgsmålene fokuserer på at forstå biomekanik, stressfordeling og resultater af TMD, samt fysioterapiens rolle og forholdet mellem TMD og andre tilstande. Dog nævnes ingen algoritmer i disse undersøgelser, hvilket indikerer, at forskningen ikke tilskriver algoritmer nogen handlekraft i besvarelsen af disse spørgsmål.
